organization.description:
Monroe County Social Services are mostly for elderly, disabled, and indigent clients, with information and referrals given to other agencies. Some emergency assistance is available on a very limited basis to those who meet the requirements. 

This department also:
* Coordinates all meetings of the Florida Keys Council for People with Disabilities. 
* Was instrumental in extending the Lower Keys Shuttle bus route from Key West to Marathon.
* Was instrumental in extending the Dade-Monroe Express bus route from Florida City to Marathon 

###MON###
organization.name: MONROE COUNTY SOCIAL SERVICES
